    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This training technique comes in six varieties, each with a different subtype, and each relating to one of your ability scores: Strength (Taijutsu), Dexterity (Taijutsu), Constitution (Chakra Control), Intelligence (Ninjutsu), Wisdom (Chakra Control) and Charisma (Genjutsu). This technique can be learned six times: Once for each ability score. You cannot learn it twice for the same ability score.<br><br>You must have previously ingested an abilityenhancing drug of the appropriate kind (such as a Strength-enhancing Shinobi drug for the Strength variation) in order to be able to complete this training, which will increase the inherent bonus granted by the drug by +1.</p>\n\n\n\n",
